tune.name: Ryan's Reel
tune.author: Mikael Georgii
tune.content:
\relative f' <<
  \new Voice {
    \clef treble
    \time 4/4
    \key d \minor

    \repeat volta 2 {
      \partial 8 a8 |
      d8 a' g a f e d cis |
      d8 c a g f e d c |
      bes4. a8 g a bes c |
      d8 e f d cis a' b cis |
      \break

      d8 a' g a f e d cis |
      d8 c a g f g a c |
      bes8 a g a bes c d f |
      a8 g e f d4.
    } \break

    \repeat volta 2 {
      a8 |
      f'8 d cis d a f' e f |
      d4. c8 d c a c |
      d8 c bes a bes a g f |
      e8 f g bes a cis d e |
      \break

      f8 d cis d a f' e f |
      d4. c8 d c a c |
      bes8 a g a bes c d f |
      a8 g e f d4.
    }
  }

  \new ChordNames {
    \chordmode {
      s8 |
      d1:m | s | g:m | d2:m a:7 |
      d1:m | s | g:m | d2:7 s4.

      s8 |
      d1:m | s | g:m | g2:m6 a:7 |
      d1:m | s | g:m | a2:7 d4.:m
    }
  }
>>
